<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>كب ورا <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وارخي رواق<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>والأشجار الباسقا ... والأطيار الناطقا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
